[The destination is fast code. This blog is about the road there.]($text.attrs('lede'))

This blog isn't really about fast code, it's about how we got there.  

SWAR tricks, bit-twiddling, branch-killing, cache-friendly layouts, the interesting part is rarely
the final benchmark or the code itself.  
It's the wrong turns, dead ends, small intuitions, and 

_"wait, why does THIS make it faster"_

moments along the way.
